text: Jiří Jakoubek (born 25 February 1960) is a Czech rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Brno
